# Venue POS — Core

## Read first
- `docs/DEVELOPMENT.md` — setup & repo layout
- `docs/TEAM_LOG.md` — what's built
- `apps/api/prisma/schema.prisma` — DB truth
- `docs/PRD.md` — user stories

## Stack
Node 20 · Fastify · Prisma 6 · PostgreSQL 16 · React 18 · Vite 5 · Electron 30 · Socket.IO 4 · Tailwind 3 · Zod · JWT RS256

## Hard rules
- POS → local-agent IPC only; offline-first sync (see `.cursor/skills/offline-sync/SKILL.md` for any new write path)
- Till writes: local SQLite + `sync_queue` + idempotent replay — not API-only
- Menu read-only on POS; Prisma for server DB
- Bilingual via `@venue-pos/i18n` + `nameEn`/`nameAr` in schema
- Update `docs/TEAM_LOG.md` after every feature
